item.title: Don Dokken
item.description: Donald Maynard Dokken is an American heavy metal vocalist, best known for being the lead singer, occasional guitarist, and founder of the band Dokken. He is known for his vibrato-laden, melodic vocal style which has made him an influential figure in American hard rock and heavy metal.

item.title: George Lynch
item.description: George Lynch is an American hard rock guitarist and songwriter. Lynch is best known for his work with heavy metal band Dokken and his post-Dokken solo band, Lynch Mob. Lynch is considered to be one of the most influential and famous 1980s metal guitarists. He is known for his unique playing style and sound. He is ranked #68 on '100 Greatest Guitarists Of All Time' by Guitar World magazine and is also ranked #10 on 'Top 10 Metal Guitarists Of All Time' by Gibson.
